@startuml component_architecture
!theme plain

title UIM SAP Event Mesh (EM) - Component Architecture

actor "Business Application / Integration" as User

node "Event Mesh Service Runtime" {
  component "EMServer\n(vibe.d REST API)" as Api
  component "EMService\n(Publish + Consume + Subscribe + Webhooks)" as Domain
  database "EMStore\n(In-Memory Data)" as Store
}

User --> Api : publish events, consume messages,\nmanage queues/topics/webhooks
Api --> Domain : routed use-case operations
Domain --> Store : persist/retrieve runtime data

note right of Domain
Capabilities:
- publish business events to topics
- route events to subscribed queues
- consume messages from queues
- webhook delivery registration
- dead letter queue management
- tenant-scoped dashboard
end note

@enduml
